ill you know how to do all these things, you’ll finish the book with a whole new appreciation for what it means to be a Texan and even more pride in saying “I’m from Texas” anywhere you wander in the world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 0aTexas - Description and travel. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh1 aDaniel, Abi.40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/30931540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781477309322423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781477309322/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK